
* oc create -f monitoring-stack.yaml
* oc create -f thanos.yaml
* oc expose service thanos-querier-eap-demo
* oc create -f service-monitor.yaml
* oc get route ha-route -o jsonpath='{"http://"}{.spec.host}{"\n"}'
* In a web browser access to the printed URL/web-clustering
* oc get route thanos-querier-eap-demo -o jsonpath='{"http://"}{.spec.host}{"\n"}'
* In a web browser access to the printed URL
* Then Execute the query: jboss_undertow_request_count_total
You should see value increasing when accessing the application

